    <item>
      <title>麦格理银行部门将停止新车贷款，专注于抵押贷款增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquaries-banking-unit-stop-new-car-loans-focus-mortgage-growth-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚金融集团麦格理集团周一表示，其银行和金融服务部门将停止通过直接、经纪人和创新租赁渠道发放新车贷款，以优先考虑住房贷款和存款业务的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquaries-banking-unit-stop-new-car-loans-focus-mortgage-growth-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激烈竞争导致盈利前景下调，新西兰航空股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-falls-after-earnings-outlook-cut-stiff-competition-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰航空周一下调了年度盈利预期，理由是经济逆风和生活成本危机导致国内和北美市场收入疲软，导致该公司股价跌至近两年低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-falls-after-earnings-outlook-cut-stiff-competition-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 01:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和美军开始年度作战演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-troops-begin-annual-combat-drills-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近 17,000 名菲律宾和美国军队将于周一在菲律宾开始为期三周的联合作战训练演习，其中包括在南中国海进行海上演习，马尼拉和北京在南海海域边界问题上发生了争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-troops-begin-annual-combat-drills-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴布亚新几内亚领导人回应拜登言论称国家不配被贴上同类相食的标签</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-responds-biden-comment-saying-nation-undeserving-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴布亚新几内亚总理詹姆斯·马拉佩表示，巴布亚新几内亚不应该被贴上食人者的标签，并在总统乔·拜登就其失踪的军人叔叔发表评论后，敦促美国清理太平洋沿岸的第二次世界大战残余物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-responds-biden-comment-saying-nation-undeserving-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:24:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚财长表示中东紧张局势加剧了对全球经济的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-treasurer-says-mideast-tensions-compound-worries-about-global-economy-2024-04-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财政部长周一警告称，中东局势加剧了人们对全球经济的担忧，并将影响政府五月份的预算，同时其主要贸易伙伴的短期前景展望将被下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-treasurer-says-mideast-tensions-compound-worries-about-global-economy-2024-04-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 23:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚法院将对寻求重新举行总统选举的请愿书做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-court-rule-petitions-seeking-presidential-election-re-run-2024-04-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚一家法院将于周一就二月总统选举结果的两项挑战做出裁决，此前落选的候选人请求重新竞选，并声称政府进行了有利于获胜者普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)的干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-court-rule-petitions-seeking-presidential-election-re-run-2024-04-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 22:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
